isa asks.&nbsp; "I think that we could provide you with some fighting machines on our own - provided you can prove to us that you will not use them for tasks that we would consider morally reprehensible."</P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P><EM><FONT color="#000000">"...That wouldn't help at all. In fact, if you did give it to me, I would think I might be tempted to use them for tasks you would consider morally wrong; despite the fact that I myself would find the actions wrong as well, this particular object is difficult to recapture..."</FONT></EM></P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P>"And the object in question?"</P>
                
            
			
