 as a result, that's why I went here. However, once it's on a 'host'...it's nearly impossible to remove by force without smashing said Toa or whatever being it's on. Problem is, I don't want to smash anyone. See the problem?"</FONT></EM></P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P>"Could you not simply turn the being intangible for long enough to remove the creature?&nbsp; And, if I may ask, what would such a creature do?"</P>
                
            
			
