 touch anything. The telekinesis I used on you isn't an option either; it has insane strength, and removing it would also require removing the body part it was on. As for what it does...it can copy the limbs of any person it has contacted, can copy the powers of whoever it is currently on flawlessly, and doesn't drain said 'hosts' energy reserves."</EM></P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P>Why I have allowed this to go on in my borders is beyond me. <img class="emoticon emoticon-joking" id="joking" src="https://lego.i.lithium.com/lego/i/emoticons/joking.png" alt="Joking" title="Joking" /></P><P>&nbsp;</P><P>They are caught by a guard post that immediately lets Rhotuka at them.</P><HR /></BLOCKQUOTE><P>OOC: What precisely do you mean by a 'guard post'?</P>
                
            
			
